{"tid":985260,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【收緊長者綜援】傳林鄭擬補鑊　60至64歲能證明自己沒有工作能力者獲千元津貼","createTime":"2019-01-17T12:28:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-17T15:55:40.000Z","uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"a65b5de93633489a10e9ddcf6d173988bf75fbe7","tid":985260,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T12:28:06.000Z","msg":"【收緊長者綜援】傳林鄭擬補鑊　60至64歲不能工作者獲千元津貼<br />\n<br />\n據悉，林鄭月娥在今早「檢討綜合社會保障援計劃」議案獲跨黨派議員支持下通過後，才邀請建制派議員今晚到特首辦商討補償方案，方案為向不能工作、年齡在60至64歲的長者提供特別津貼。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">消息指，提出的方案預料為60至64歲、能證明自己沒有工作能力的長者，提供1,030元的津貼，金額相等於長者綜援與成人綜援的差額。</span>方案內容雖然已有，但具體如何執行、何時執行及公布等等詳情就暫時未知。<br />\n<br />\n非建制議員聯署　要求擱置「長者綜援資格調高至65歲的措施」<br />\n<br />\n另一邊廂，26位非建制派立法會議員包括熱血公民鄭松泰、醫學界議員陳沛然今聯署，批評政府在議案通過後只約見建制派議員「試圖拆彈補鑊」，稱對做法感到憤怒；26位議員又要求特首林鄭月娥盡早安排會面，檢討綜援的長遠安排，並立即擱置「長者綜援資格調高至65歲的措施」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/284258/收緊長者綜援-傳林鄭擬補鑊-60至64歲不能工作者獲千元津貼\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F284258%2F%E6%94%B6%E7%B7%8A%E9%95%B7%E8%80%85%E7%B6%9C%E6%8F%B4-%E5%82%B3%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E6%93%AC%E8%A3%9C%E9%91%8A-60%E8%87%B364%E6%AD%B2%E4%B8%8D%E8%83%BD%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E8%80%85%E7%8D%B2%E5%8D%83%E5%85%83%E6%B4%A5%E8%B2%BC&d=dUlPXj5JBOIv%2Bq9kYmFrqL%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=5d86d078\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/284258/收緊長者綜援-傳林鄭擬補鑊-60至64歲不能工作者獲千元津貼</a>"},{"pid":"ada7f53c47c14a472fec28bffb656b1882e1a329","tid":985260,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T12:29:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee98a76de4476f8b0895ba7e06637e87000cab3c","tid":985260,"uid":8439,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T12:29:55.000Z","msg":"點證明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本身真係做唔到野果班已經拎緊綜援啦"},{"pid":"b9cac0d06817e34382f6663785c00bc1780ecebd","tid":985260,"uid":36901,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T12:30:45.000Z","msg":"八婆當人白癡<br />\n完全冇工作能力早就合乎傷殘豁免啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af378e88101229afecd9dff5fb45a3bb0ad05d08","tid":985260,"uid":35790,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T12:34:17.000Z","msg":"如要醫生肯寫紙證明無工作能力<br />\n已經可以申請嚴重傷殘津貼<br />\n因為獲普通傷殘津貼者<br />\n仍未失去工作能力"},{"pid":"8aea578b9776b98150c335185cd8a2c05bf39e11","tid":985260,"uid":36901,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T12:34:26.000Z","msg":"btw<br />\ncctvb話只要向社工表明持續搵工<br />\n就可以補返差額<br />\n<br />\n呢個乜撚野政策,玩9死前線社工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59e2b5799da8b1d641f157e32269fdb425b85271","tid":985260,"uid":38757,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T12:34:53.000Z","msg":"佢唔明白做佢個果位要點應付上面同下面"},{"pid":"fa29eaefab05508285c0ac82a0124332421504a1","tid":985260,"uid":124410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T12:35:36.000Z","msg":"on9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8e89a11e881fde1df328c75ec9f41933b6119a7","tid":985260,"uid":35790,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T12:37:34.000Z","msg":"我唔識用八達通搭mtr<br />\n堅離地特首"},{"pid":"56075dc88b777903abcbb727fef62ebe7fa7965e","tid":985260,"uid":33432,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T12:41:54.000Z","msg":"成日搞到咁多麻煩審查<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一係就大方啲，一係就度縮到底啦<br />\n又要扮闊佬又要戴幾廿萬個頭盔可以派少一個得一個咁<br />\n核撚突突<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f6369eddb32385667f5d211818aa194686c8762","tid":985260,"uid":155137,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T12:42:40.000Z",